        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A hag long ago cursed your family, or you are a descendant of a hag or changeling, and their accursed corruption infests your blood and soul.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> occult</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Deception, Occultism</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Daze], 1st: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Illusory Disguise], 2nd: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Stupefy], 3rd: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Blindness], 4th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Outcast's Curse], 5th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Mariner's Curse], 6th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Cursed Metamorphosis], 7th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Warp Mind], 8th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Spiritual Epidemic], 9th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Nature's Enmity]</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Jealous Hex], advanced: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Horrific Visage], greater: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.You're Mine]</p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> Spiteful curses punish your foes. You deal 2 mental damage per spell level (basic Will save) to the first creature that deals damage to you before the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Hag Blood Magic]</p>"
